/: Root Directory.

/adm		'secure' directory.  Subdirectory structure is similar to /.
/cmd            command directory.
/d              domain directory.
/data           data directory, i.e. 'save' directory.
/doc            documentation directory.
/pub            public (ftp) directory.
/include        header file directory.
/log            log file directory.
/obj            object directory; all objects are below this.
/tmp            temporary directory; world writable
/u              user directory; contains save files and home directories.
